channel.title: Missing files when i download Moparscape
channel.description:
[b]I have downloaded Moparscape and i dont have client.java , worldodject and thing like that...
When i open the moparscape folder i see this ,
all_IDs (folder) Aryan (folder) HybridScape (folder) Music (folder) MoparScape (executable jar file) readme (.text) runMoparScape(MS-DOS batch file) runMoparScape-linux.sh (sh file) _____________________________ And in the all_IDs (folder) i see this
Items (XML) Npcs (XML) Objects (XML) ______________________________ And in the Aryan Folder i dont have the client.java and worldobject and things like that... and in HybridScape i dont have it... how can i have it?
Thanks for help[/b]
